      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It is in truly incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! I've absolutely babied this car, keeping it spotless inside and out, and it drives like a total dream. If you've been looking for a ride that\u2019s been cared for with a ton of love, this is the one. Come take a look and let's get you behind the wheel!",
