    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the closest you will find to a brand-new car without the dealership markup. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen a drop of rain. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with no creasing or bolster wear, and the high-gloss trim is free of any micro-scratches. Every electronic feature, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium sound system, functions with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive folder of service records from the same certified technician since day one. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of road salt or oxidation. This is a true collector-grade example for a buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
